  "text": "IV. NUMERICAL VERIFICATION In order to verify the theoretical developments shown in previous sections, circuit simulations are carried out by Sim-PowerSystems of Matlab considering three-, fiveand seven-phase inverters supplying sinusoidal balanced current sources as in (1) -1 according to [CITATION_1] . The harmonic spectrum of the voltage error is shown in all cases up to 19 th harmonic component.",
